# Wiki log

Chronological record of all wiki changes. Format:

```
## [YYYY-MM-DD] [action] | [description]
```

Action vocabulary: `create`, `update`, `refactor`, `delete`, `move`, `rename`, `decide`, `setup`, `fix`, `research`, `tidy`, `draft`, `discovery`.

One entry per meaningful change. Append at the bottom of the file (newest last), or prepend at the top (newest first) — pick one convention at Phase 3 and stay consistent.

